Package: ANNlight
Type: Package
Title: A Lightweight, low dependency R-package for artificial neural networks
Version: 0.1
Date: 2022-08-01
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Steffen", family = "Köhler", email = "steffen.koehler@rub.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Steffen Köhler <steffen.koehler@rub.de>
Description: Providing basic functionality of a neural net, without having to worry about a large
    number of dependencies. In fact, the aim is for 'R6' to stay the only dependency, because the code is written object-oriented.
